<blockquote>
<p>“An exit is just an easy way out.”<br />
― Anthony T. Hincks</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Part two.</p>
<p>Many thanks to Soulless, Kalinin, Lazar, CaptainKirby, ARD, Hippo, Yossi, Westrin, and anyone else who had eyes on this throughout the process of writing it. There is work still to be done here, and this is a step towards that.</p>
<hr />
<h2><span>Image Credits</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>The file &quot;exterior.jpg&quot; is taken from <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Factory_in_the_snow_-_geograph.org.uk_-_1276616.jpg">here</a> and is licensed under creative commons.</li>
<li>The file &quot;drdesmet.jpg&quot; is taken from <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Cory_Robbins,_circa_early_1980s.jpg">here</a> and is licensed under creative commons.</li>
<li>The file &quot;destroyed.png&quot; is taken from <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Destroyed_steel_factory_near_Corral_-_Photo_from_the_autumn_of_1960.png">here</a> and is licensed under creative commons.</li>
<li>The file &quot;accelerator.jpg&quot; is taken from <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Joe_Moore,_Photographer._September,_1996._BEVATRON_ROOF_SHIELDING_AND_BUILDING_TRUSS_STRUCTURE_-_University_of_California_Radiation_Laboratory,_Bevatron,_1_Cyclotron_Road,_HAER_CAL,1-BERK,4-71.tif">here</a> and is licensed under creative commons.</li>
<li>The file &quot;01_solitude.jpg&quot; is taken from <a href="http://damianjmcdonald.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/01_solitude.jpg">here</a> and has been authorized for my use in this article by the original artist, Damien J. McDonald, and is otherwise All Rights Reserved. More of Damien's work can be seen at www.damianjmcdonald.com.</li>
<li>Lastly, the images &quot;darkbodyclassified.png&quot; and &quot;darkbodywarning.png&quot; are original creations of mine, released under Creative Commons.</li>
</ul>

